05:31.113 --> 05:33.071
<i>♪ Still at odds
with the Irish mob ♪</i>

05:33.202 --> 05:35.770
<i>♪ Rolls-Royce down
Malcolm X Boulevard ♪</i>

05:35.900 --> 05:38.990
<i>♪ Lord, these-- really
out here preyin' on me ♪</i>

05:39.121 --> 05:41.558
<i>♪ Got the .40 on me
and his hand on me ♪</i>

05:41.689 --> 05:43.821
<i>♪ Snow-white mink
like I'm Dutch Schultz ♪</i>

05:43.952 --> 05:46.868
<i>♪ Run the books and let me
show you how the numbers look ♪</i>

05:46.998 --> 05:49.610
<i>♪ You can't be lucky
like you Luciano ♪</i>

05:49.740 --> 05:52.352
<i>♪ The kilos slammin'
like they new pianos ♪</i>

05:52.482 --> 05:54.963
<i>♪ And Fat Boy got the big body</i>

05:55.093 --> 05:57.139
<i>♪ Coast-to-coast,
